<P>
By MARYANN HUDSON 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Darryl Strawberry will be released from a drug treatment center this week, 
perhaps as soon as today, but his plans as far as the Dodgers are concerned 
remain unknown. 
</P>
<P>
 "I don't think anybody knows," said Michael Strawberry, Darryl's 
brother."Darryl hasn't talked with (the Dodgers) or anything, and they need to 
figure out what to do as an organization and go from there." 
</P>
<P>
