to do when Strawberry is ready to return to play. They are paying him $3 
million this season and owe another $5 million for next season, the last of his 
contract. Their options include releasing him with pay, trading him -- perhaps 
picking up a portion of his salary to do so -- allowing him to return or 
finding a way to void his contract. MARYANN HUDSON 
