taken to Los Robles Regional Medical Center. Both were in serious condition, a 
nursing supervisor said. 
</P>
<P>
 The other pedestrian, Maria Hernandez, 16, of Moorpark, was taken to Simi 
Valley Hospital, where she was treated and released. 
