11.19 14.08 80 Piru 9.81 16.59 59 Santa Paula 13.00 16.91 77 Simi Valley 9.27 
14.89 62 Thousand Oaks 9.64 13.89 69 Ventura Govt. Center 10.98 15.49 71  
</P>
