Schering-Plough 71-51 3/4 64 +3 5/8 +6.0 Merck 44 1/8-28 1/8 31 1/8 +1 1/2 +5.1 
Eli Lilly 62-43 5/8 51 5/8 +2 3/8 +4.8 Pfizer 75 5/8-52 1/2 61 1/8 +2 1/8 +3.6 
