REGIONAL EARNINGS: CALIFORNIA AMPLIFIER LOSES $86,000 IN 4TH QUARTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 California Amplifier Inc., a Camarillo maker of components for satellite and 
wireless cable systems, reported a loss of $86,000 for its fiscal fourth 
quarter, contrasted with a profit of $840,000 in the comparable period a year 
earlier. 
</P>
