too accommodating to the media, fans and his teammates. 
</P>
<P>
 "I thought I could do it like Michael Jordan and some of those other guys," 
Bonds said. "But I can't do both things. My teammates have told me, 'Don't be 
nice for us.' " 
</P>
<P>
