<HEADLINE>
<P>
ATHLETES OF THE WEEK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Misty Lauby 
</P>
<P>
 El Toro, Sr. 
</P>
<P>
 Softball / Pitcher 
</P>
<P>
 As a sophomore, Lauby led the Chargers to the semifinals of the Southern 
Section playoffs.Last season, the Chargers failed to make the playoffs. After 
struggling last season, Lauby has regained her dominating form. Wednesday, 
Lauby struck out 20 in a 3-0 victory over Mission Viejo. She allowed one hit -- 
a bunt single in the first inning -- and walked one. She struck out eight in a 
row twice. Friday, against Capistrano Valley, she pitched a three-hitter with 
eight strikeouts in a 5-0 victory. Lauby has signed with Northwestern. Other 
notables: 
</P>
