victory over Fullerton. 
</P>
<P>
 * Debbie Goddu, Whittier Christian, pitched her fourth consecutive shutout in 
a 1-0 victory over Brethren Christian. She also scored the game's only run. 
</P>
<P>
 * Brandee McArthur, Villa Park, pitched a one-hitter with 16 strikeouts in a 
1-0 victory over El Modena. 
</P>
